{
  "stem": "23815.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then they took some young boys, young men, Jewish people, to take the bodies [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] from the-- from the-- from the-- the gas rooms and take the bodies and put them inside the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Every week [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they used to take those boys, put it on the wall, and shoot them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why they did that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they didn't know the world to know what's happening there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After another week, brought other few boys, new ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every week they had to change those boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were from all the country in the world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean-- and every time before they went to be shot, they used to-- used to sing the anthem from their own country, because they knew they was going to be shot and they want to-- to sing it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they sing the anthem from their own country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then-- then we knew it, what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Soon we heard the anthem, we knew there was going to be shots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And every-- and every time we-- we knew it, that-- that there is singing the anthem, here we knew it was going to be those shots again.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was going on-- every week they used to change those boys, because they were afraid in case some of them will be alive one day, and they will tell the story.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But the screams, that was unbearable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was much too much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And every day coming, people and people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know, so many people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were six million Jews, they say, coming all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And do you know what else we did?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
